    <h3 itemprop="headline">Indiana sheriff's deputy shot three times in hospital ER after stopping to help stranded motorist</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      An Indiana sheriff&apos;s deputy was shot three times in a hospital emergency room by a suspect he had helped as a stranded motorist, authorities say.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/05/22/indiana-sheriffs-deputy-shot-three-times-hospital-er-stopping-help-stranded-motorist/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
