        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Fake Geek Squad billing scam email: Red flags and how to avoid</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A fraudulent Geek Squad billing email using Razorpay branding is pressuring consumers to click payment links and hand over sensitive personal information.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/05/21/fake-geek-squad-billing-scam-email-red-flags-how-avoid/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
