        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Samsung's union puts off strike after reaching last-minute wage deal with management</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Samsung Electronics’ labor union says it’ll hold off a planned strike and put a tentative wage deal with management to a vote.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/05/20/samsung-faces-strike-after-pay-talks-with-union-fall-apart/"  >(Kim Tong-Hyung, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
