    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Google launches Gemini 3.5 Flash to push AI agents deeper into enterprise workflows</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Google has launched Gemini 3.5 Flash, a new AI model designed to support agentic workflows across its products and enterprise platforms, as the company looks to move generative AI beyond chatbot-style interactions and deeper into business operations.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/05/20/google-launches-gemini-3-5-flash-to-push-ai-agents-deeper-into-enterprise-workflows/"  >(Info World)</a>
    </p>
