        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">AntV data visualization tool the latest to be hit by ongoing npm supply chain attacks</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The world’s largest open-source registry, node package manager (npm), has been hit by another fast-moving malware attack, this time targeting the widely-used AntV enterprise data visualization tool.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/05/19/antv-data-visualization-tool-the-latest-to-be-hit-by-ongoing-npm-supply-chain-attacks/"  >(Info World)</a>
    </p>
