    <p itemprop="text">
      Yankees ace Gerrit Cole pitched six shutout innings in his return from elbow ligament reconstruction that caused a 569-day absence.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2026/05/23/gerrit-cole-pitches-6-shutout-innings-for-yanks-after-569-day-absence-returning-from-elbow-surgery/"  >(Ronald Blum, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
