    <h3 itemprop="headline">Detroit Pistons&#8217; Ausar Thompson named First-Team All-Defense, first player honored since Ben Wallace</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Detroit Pistons forward Ausar Thompson has been named to the 2025-26 Kia NBA All-Defensive First Team, becoming the first Pistons player to earn the honor in 20 years.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2026/05/23/detroit-pistons-ausar-thompson-named-first-team-all-defense-first-player-honored-since-ben-wallace/"  >(Brandon Carr, Local 4)</a>
