    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump drops IRS lawsuit, paving the way for a settlement</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The president sued the IRS and the Treasury Department in January, demanding $10 billion over the leak of his tax returns years ago.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/05/18/npr-trump-irs-lawsuit-settlement/"  >(Carrie Johnson, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
