  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 22 May 2026 18:31:53 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Matt Sepic, MPR News Staff, and Kyra Miles, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/05/22/minnesota-fraud-charges-from-trump-administration.webp" alt="Feds: 15 charged with bilking Medicaid in Minnesota" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Feds: 15 charged with bilking Medicaid in Minnesota</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Federal authorities on Thursday alleged that more than $90 million was stolen from seven state-managed Medicaid programs, including one meant to help children with autism and another intended to help vulnerable people find stable homes.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/05/22/minnesota-fraud-charges-from-trump-administration/"  >(Matt Sepic, MPR News Staff, and Kyra Miles, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 19 May 2026 18:35:04 GMT">
